@startuml Functional UML Diagram - Order Placement
start
:User browses catalog;
:User searches/filters lots;
if (User logged in?) then (no)
  :Redirect to login/register;
  :User logs in or registers;
else (yes)
endif
:User views lot details;
if (Add to cart?) then (yes)
  :Add lot to cart;
  :Update cart total;
else (no)
endif
if (Add to favorites?) then (yes)
  :Add to favorites;
else (no)
endif
:User proceeds to checkout;
:Review cart items;
:Enter shipping details;
:Select payment method;
:Confirm order;
:Create order record;
:Update lot status to reserved;
:Send confirmation email;
:Redirect to order tracking;
stop
@enduml</content>
